lines.text: I'm looking for a guy named Louie, fuzzy hair, crooked teeth, bug eyes. Has he been around lately?
Have you ever made love to a woman until she lost consciousness?
He was kinda of cute... for a sociopath.
Brent? He's been trained for this since he was a sperm.

[Preparing her rope for the absail down the side of the building]
You don't think we're going overboard?
To sailor- you, i want to talk to you.
Well, aren't we looking charming tonight.
Ellie, I had so much fun tonight. We got drunk, we almost got mugged, I met a sailor with a big fish.
